children.subject: If time affords it, you should take Stat 134 or Stat 140! It's the next best thing after 126 in terms of probability preparation for 189, and it also counts as a requirement (elective) for the major!
I would say it's definitely worth taking 126 after 189. 126 is a bit broader than 189 and it also gives you a really strong understanding of probability. it's a really good base to have

history.content:
I'm planning on taking 189 next sem but I'm very rusty on my probability from CS 70 and I know that is a very important part of the course. Any insight on how to prepare?

Also an additional question: is it worth taking 126/127 after 189?
